> @puneet has this (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/38379#issuecomment-1495407686) been resolved?
@fernando I am currently trying to reproduce this error, I do have a probable fix which I am trying to test. This issue can happen in sandboxes where metrics-server was installed manually.
Another way to fix this can be to delete the manually installed metrics server and re run the pipeline.
